Output ../gifs/rcc-menu.gif
Set Theme "Ayu Mirage"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 800
Set Height 600
Set Padding 32
Set Framerate 12
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.5
Hide
Type "cd $HOME/Raccoon" Enter
Type "alias rcc=$HOME/Raccoon/rcc" Enter
Show

Type "rcc" Sleep 500ms Enter
Sleep 2s
Type "1" Enter
Sleep 2s
Type "q" Enter
Sleep 1s
